# Hostinger Business — Node.js Selector (Passenger) routing.
# Passenger picks up the Node app automatically once you configure it in
# hPanel → Advanced → Node.js. This .htaccess just makes sure Apache hands
# every request to Passenger instead of trying to serve files directly.
PassengerEnabled on

# If Passenger ever fails to start, fall back to a clear error instead of
# Apache exposing the raw filesystem.
DirectoryIndex disabled
Options -Indexes
